  "logTail": [
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "You open your eyes. Straw beneath you, the smell of wet rice, a low roof you do not know. A cold spring — the ninth year of An'ei — though the year is as lost to you as your name.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"You're awake.\" Sōan the physician sits back on his heels. \"No kami carried you off, whatever the village wants to believe. A flood took you, and a blow to the head took the rest. Bodies forget. Given work and rice, they also mend.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Sōan"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "You take stock of yourself: bruised, hollow, half-starved — but breathing.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "Rice lies scattered across the Kurosawa grain-store floor. Spilled stores are waste — and clearing waste is a kind of work, if you set your hands to it.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"What happened to me?\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "You"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"You washed up below the weir three days back, a gash on your scalp and no name to give. The river does that. We fished you out; the rest you'll have to earn back.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Sōan"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"There was a road. Grey rain. A name I can't hold. Is that the fever?\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "You"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"That is the blow talking, not a ghost. It will fade — or it won't. Don't let the old women make a haunting of it.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Sōan"
    },
    {
      "channel": "milestone",
      "text": "Perk unlocked — A Waking Fragment: A half-caught omen that bends fortune your way, though your step is slower to answer. (+1 LUCK / −1 AGI)",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "Something surfaces and is gone — a porter's knot, a road in grey rain, a name you cannot keep hold of.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"Hold the road. The rain. Almost a name.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "You"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "You chase it inward — and the ache in your skull chases you back. The name stays lost, but the habit of looking sets in.",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "milestone",
      "text": "Perk unlocked — The Inward Turn: A mind that deepens by dwelling, at the price of a slower body. (+1 INT / −1 SPD)",
      "count": 1
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "On your feet, then. I am Genemon, steward of this house, and I keep the little it has left to keep. You'll not remember any of it, so hear it plain: the Kurosawa are samurai still — on the lord's rolls, if nowhere in the granary.",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"What house is this?\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "You"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"The Kurosawa. A great name gone to seed — samurai on the rolls, paupers in the granary. I've kept it upright since the last master could not, and I'll keep it upright when you can't either.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "(You say nothing, and reach for the spilled rice.)",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "You"
    },
    {
      "channel": "narration",
      "text": "\"...A man who works before he talks. Rare. We'll get on.\"",
      "count": 1,
      "speaker": "Genemon"
    },
    {
      "channel": "milestone",
      "text": "Perk unlocked — Hands Before Words: A steady quickness that answers with work — trusting to no luck. (+1 SPD / −1 LUCK)",
      "count": 1
    }
  ],
  "save": ""
}